# [IANABIS](../wg/ianabis.html)

## Summary

The IANABIS working group met at IETF 126 in Vienna to discuss updates on guideline and procedural drafts for IANA considerations. The session was chaired by Murray Kucherawy and Ted Hardie. Key topics discussed included the introduction of three proposed sub-policies for "Specification Required" registration procedures to combat registry squatting and specify "permanent and readily available" requirements, and status updates on `draft-ietf-ianabis-rfc7120bis` and `draft-ietf-ianabis-rfc8126bis`.

